- remove "quantity" from "order"
- add "payment_info" and "shipping_info" to "user"
- add "add_to_cart" to "products"

- creat "cart" table
  - product_id
  - user_id
  - quantity
  - status
    - carted?, purchased?, removed?
  - order_id (optional)
- creat CRUD action for "cart"

- connect all via associations
  - cart
    - belongs_to user
    - belongs_to order
  - user
    - has_many carts
    - has_many orders, through: :cart
  - order
    - has_many cart
    - has_many users, through: :cart
